Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.90,0:00:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it wasn't just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.70,0:00:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to see Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.56,0:00:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.64,0:00:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.56,0:00:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:04.54,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:06.41,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:07.28,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.41,0:02:07.28,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:08.65,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:10.32,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:11.35,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.35,0:02:12.81,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Yadomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:13.80,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:19.60,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:21.99,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,One Menma is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:24.28,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:24.30,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:25.99,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.07,0:02:28.14,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:31.30,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:35.96,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,You tried going to school the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:41.96,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Those girls didn't really mean what they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:43.74,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,C-Could you give them anothe—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:45.70,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I don't really care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:46.64,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:48.34,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:55.83,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Nothing you or your friends say will affect my life in any way, shape, or form.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:58.09,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,What the heck?! That's not cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:03:00.23,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I wasn't trying to be cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:01.65,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I'm not like my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:04.08,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,W-Wait up, Yadomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.75,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:14.36,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:15.34,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Stop messing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:18.00,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:26.20,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Yadomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:31.22,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,If that were to happen to you, too... with everything as it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:32.90,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Just like with Menma...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:39.04,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Hey, Menma showed up at your place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:44.35,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,So, you did like Menma... didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:46.05,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,What are you saying....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:53.80,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,{instead of 'normally can't be seen' -> normally invisible OR normally not there)}You can see something that no one else can because you really, really liked her... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:59.42,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,You said it was fine to believe in her just a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.11,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,I don't really understand, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:04.52,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,If you can see Menma,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:07.05,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,be nice to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:10.35,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,I don't really understand, but please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:15.44,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Jintan, can you see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:16.49,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:17.90,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:23.51,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,So, we couldn't find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:27.37,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,How boring. I wanted to see her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:33.18,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Welcome back. The meat's grilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.55,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Yukiatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.80,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Yay! Meaty meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:37.12,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Why were you up here by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:38.49,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.49,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,It looks tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:40.00,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Because Menma asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:46.34,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,When Menma appeared before me, she said,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.96,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,"Please don't make a bigger fuss out of this."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:51.80,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Menma seriously said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:54.06,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I couldn't make it out completely,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:59.19,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,but don't you think it would actually bother her if all of you got worked up over some wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:02.98,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,That's not true! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:10.19,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Ever since you all have gotten together and started to remember me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:14.17,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I'm a lot more happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:19.88,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Even if I'm dead, I want everyone to get along!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:22.91,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,So, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:27.46,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Hey... if Menma said that, then maybe we should just stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:30.24,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.76,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,That's not what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:42.24,Default,Jinta,0,0,0,,H-Hey, guys. Try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:44.26,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Is that muffin bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:47.32,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Oh! That brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:50.01,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Jintan's mom used to make that for us all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:52.01,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:52.91,Default,Jintan,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:56.85,Default,Jintan,0,0,0,,something that Menma made.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:06:01.02,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:03.16,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:08.07,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Are you saying that a {\i1}ghost{\i0} made muffin bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:11.93,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Now that's definitely taking it too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:14.02,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Don't you think so, too, Hisakawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:18.78,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Er... I think it's pretty original, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:20.55,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:24.86,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I don't care if you think I'm weird or crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:30.65,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma's actually saying that she'll be happy if we're still together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:34.26,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,That she'll be happy if we don't forget about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:37.35,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:39.21,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Just stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:43.03,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,You can't forget about Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:45.09,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,You're forever obsessed with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:47.02,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,You're so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:50.53,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Man, looks like I brought everyone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.64,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Just eat it all yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.22,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Hey, Yukiatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:58.14,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.60,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I'll head back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:03.41,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Everyone can eat the muffin bread together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:04.95,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Then it won't really be everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:06.00,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Yadomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.59,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,All things aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:14.60,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,This is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:15.19,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:15.91,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:19.68,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,What was the Menma you saw like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:23.41,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Let's see, she was in a white one-piece dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:26.70,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Did she have a small ribbon attached around this area?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:32.45,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Huh? I can't really remember, but I think she may have...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.13,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Wait, how did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.27,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Did you see Menma, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:37.25,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:41.01,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,You're such a mysterious girl, Tsuruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:44.98,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,So juicy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:58.96,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Hey, Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:02.66,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I wonder what the Menma that Yukiatsu saw was like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:03.50,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:08.69,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,If I'm Mario Menma, then the other one must be Luigi Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:11.21,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,It'd be fun if it was a 2-player game. Right, Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:13.19,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:35.49,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Man, what the hell was Yukiatsu saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:38.85,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,"Menma said not to make a fuss." Yeah, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.62,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,He's got one hell of an imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:45.23,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I guess that applies to me even more so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:54.92,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I can't forget about it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:59.39,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,The way he twisted Menma's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.34,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:06.00,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,So, you did like Menma... didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:10.33,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.57,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jinta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.57,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:20.14,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,We stopped by because we heard a good boy named Jinta lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:22.83,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,What's this? My good boy radar is going off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.87,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Beep beep beep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.30,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Hey, Menma...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:27.44,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,We're not Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:30.60,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,We're a stuffed animal and a Kokeshi spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.05,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.55,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I'm really Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:37.70,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,"Really" Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:44.79,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,You really don't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:45.96,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Whaaat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:47.81,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:51.72,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Stop it, Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:57.60,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Hey, Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:10:01.27,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,You like Menma... don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:05.36,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Hey, Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:06.16,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:11.60,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Forget it. Let's go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.11,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I'm turning off the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:14.48,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:34.86,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:36.95,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.05,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,How did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:42.53,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,really feel about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.55,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:01.19,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,A one-piece dress with a ribbon on the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:15.15,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I'm off to work, Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:20.11,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Jintan, I think the bill collector will come today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:23.95,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Give him the money from the top drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:24.61,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:26.05,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:27.83,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:33.98,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:36.51,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:43.95,Default,TV,0,0,0,,There will be a string of hot days ahead, but as for me... {timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:43.95,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Wow, this guy thinks of some weird stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:44.97,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:49.53,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,she hasn't said anything about me not going back to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:52.05,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,You'll fall! You'll fall! Be careful! That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:54.45,Default,TV,0,0,0,,Oh, I feel great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:54.45,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,A visitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:55.75,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Is it the bill collector?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:56.90,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:58.83,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Tsuruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:11:59.94,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:02.20,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,What are you... What about school?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.59,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Oh, we're getting ready for the culture festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.34,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:07.83,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,My class is doing an {\i1}a capella{\i0} kadaoke cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:09.80,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Don't you think that's stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:10.72,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:11.85,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,May I come inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:13.06,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:14.28,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:16.02,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:20.36,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,This place hasn't changed. How nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:25.15,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Hey, why do you have the kotatsu on a wooden floor in your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:26.27,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Why would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:30.10,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Sweets, Jintan! You have to give your guest sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:36.66,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Hey, all I've got are some cookies. {Country Ma'am brand}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:37.74,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,That muffin bread...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:38.94,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:44.05,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,It was more stiff than the kind your mom made.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:45.00,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:48.41,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,I think the flour wasn't sifted properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:52.42,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,If you add baking powder, it'll be more fluffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:57.63,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Wow! So its bad taste wasn't because it didn't have raisins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.79,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I didn't know you could cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:04.33,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Anyone can cook if they know the recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:06.05,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.75,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,You just have to get the portions and timing right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:13.99,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,As long as you avoid stumbling in odd places that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:20.78,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Why'd you come here? I have a bad feeling about your visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:22.68,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,What're you saying, Jintan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:28.50,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,I'll cut to the chase. I don't believe that Menma made this muffin bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:35.15,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I thought as much. How could I expect you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:40.45,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,But that's exactly why I have a request for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:48.31,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,So what do you think he said?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:51.52,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,"You smell great, but I bet your armpits smell even better!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:53.09,Default,Girl1,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:55.54,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,I mean what kind of pick-up line is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:56.21,Default,Girl1,0,0,0,,How creepy.  {timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.20,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,You think he had an armpit fetish? {not sure about this}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:01.80,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,Hey, Naruko, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:04.11,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Sorry, I just remembered something I need to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:09.69,Default,Girl1,0,0,0,,Hey, don't you think Naruko's been kind of unsociable lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:13.87,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know what you mean. It kind of pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:19.00,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,That's Yadomi, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:26.05,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Can't you tell by looking at that lump of lethargy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:29.04,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:31.53,Default,Tusur,0,0,0,,It's a Super Peace Busters engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:35.59,Default,Tusur,0,0,0,,We're busting false peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:41.75,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Hey, Jintan. Are you really going to do it? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:45.64,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I, myself, don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:54.38,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:57.04,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:00.81,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:02.21,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Second semester has started.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:05.01,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Can you afford to stroll around town like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:11.95,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma kept bugging me to go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:17.78,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Hey, tell me what the Menma you saw was like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.80,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,My Menma is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.55,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,That's the wrong way to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:36.33,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,The Menma in my house is saying yours is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:39.80,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,We're all going to the secret base now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:42.33,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,And I'll bring Menma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:44.55,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,If you'd like you can come too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:47.66,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,You're getting carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:48.35,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:52.65,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,This isn't like the old days when you played leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:57.77,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,And even back then I didn't acknowledge you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:02.35,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Don't talk to me like we're friends, you whipped dog. {OR whipped dog -> loser; but, I kept it like this to make Menma's joke later work}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:11.89,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:15.12,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Nice, Yadomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.04,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.81,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Come out, Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:32.23,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:34.78,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:37.10,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,to him. {why am I getting a hannibal vibe here}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:44.56,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,You didn't have to go out of your way to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:48.07,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,I was free anyway. Give it a rest already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:53.00,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Want to try this? Bugs were biting me all over after the barbecue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:56.30,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Why don't you show less skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:17:00.65,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,You're not a whipped dog; you're a top dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:59.72,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Why should I? This is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:02.76,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,So, either way, I'm a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:06.62,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Maybe the Menma that Yukiatsu saw isn't fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:07.50,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:11.64,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Think about it, it wouldn't be that strange for another Menma to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:19.45,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,After all, I don't even know why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:27.49,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Huh? Why's everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.48,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Is this your party night?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:31.52,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Just hurry up and turn your headlight off, it's too bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:33.70,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Oh. Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.25,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:38.78,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Much better than canned coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:41.97,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,This is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:45.35,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,My parents bought a new one at the bazaar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:48.51,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,I'm sorry it's used, but you can use it here if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:51.01,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,You're such a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:52.05,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:55.51,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,And you even thought to bring cups...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:59.35,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. I have a collection of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:59.35,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,It really is fun when everyone's together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:01.16,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Is that your hobby or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:03.51,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Is something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:04.18,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I have so much fun doing this with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:05.29,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:08.54,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Not really. I just think it's old-fashioned.  {timing check might be going too far}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:07.36,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:08.52,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Men—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:09.80,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:11.42,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Let's let Menma drink some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:14.75,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Right, Jintan? Are you here, Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:17.73,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Are you here? Or maybe over here? Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:18.90,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:20.19,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Hey, Poppo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:24.06,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I thought about it after the barbecue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:29.39,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Didn't Menma say she'd be happy if everyone got together?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.12,0:18:33.84,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,That defines Menma perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.87,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I really get what she means.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:37.84,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Poppo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:41.85,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,She said she doesn't want to be forgotten, but it's not like we could ever forget her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:44.85,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,She's such a little worrywart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:49.10,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Poppo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:49.47,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:50.57,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:52.26,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Something feels kind of heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:57.44,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I'm shivering! Did I drink too much coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.17,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I gotta go to the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:00.39,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I'm coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:02.55,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Let's go pee together! {so apparently there's a word in japanese for going to pee together...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:04.47,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,"You can't forget about Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:08.05,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,"You're forever obsessed with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:10.14,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,"You're so pathetic."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:13.41,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Tsuruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:17.95,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Yukiatsu was talking about himself when he said all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:25.44,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,W-What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:24.74,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:26.30,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Your fly is wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:28.78,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Forget about that. She was there! I saw her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:29.10,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:30.76,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:38.92,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Over here! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:42.87,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Hey, are you sure you saw her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:45.89,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Yeah, I double-checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:48.06,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,You know, about what Tsuruko mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:48.79,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:53.59,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,The one-piece dress. It had a ribbon around here right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:58.98,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,A one-piece dress with a ribbon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:01.18,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:03.00,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Look at that Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:08.98,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:10.78,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,That's her! It's Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:12.09,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,It is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.42,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:17.07,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Be careful out there, Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:28.41,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Hey, Menma! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:32.54,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,I... I can't go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:35.00,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.79,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,I... I just need a quick break.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:38.55,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,How's it look, Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:41.40,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,She was here a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:46.07,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,That's that, then. Let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:50.95,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,You can shave your legs, but you still have a man's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:53.38,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,You can only go so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:55.30,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Yukiatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:58.54,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:00.63,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:03.31,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:05.48,Default,Anal,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:23.20,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:26.19,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Did you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.19,0:21:27.18,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:36.11,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yukiatsu...
