Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:21.01,Opening,,0,0,0,,{\an8}zutto kimi wo sagashiteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:25.14,Opening,,0,0,0,,{\an8}souyatte ima wa boku no hou e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:28.81,Opening,,0,0,0,,{\an8}toitsumeru koto mo nakute
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:35.61,Opening,,0,0,0,,{\an8}mada futari wa sugu soko ni irunoni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:43.37,Opening,,0,0,0,,{\an8}douka mata aemasuyouni nante
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:51.50,Opening,,0,0,0,,{\an8}douka shiteru mitai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:36.34,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,Upon pages and pages of entries
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:40.52,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,We've put down all our emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:43.77,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,But now I've hit a writer's block
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:47.77,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to finish this page anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.02,0:00:50.94,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,Putting a bookmark in my diary
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:55.99,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,You and I go out to ride the bike we found in the dumpster
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:59.16,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,Let's go to our secret place
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:03.50,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,Where we piled up our bricks of memories
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:08.75,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,Run up the hill, where we can see the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:13.30,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,Where we can see the sky so fearfully blue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:16.51,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,With cider in my right hand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:21.01,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,My other hand helps me search for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:25.14,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,You used to come find me way back when
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:28.81,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,You used to demand me of so much more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:35.61,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,You're both still standing right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:43.37,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,Yet why do I pray to see you both again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:51.50,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,There must be something off with me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:30.56,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\an8}deai wa futtoshita shunkan
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:37.19,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kaerimichi no kousaten de koe wo kaketekureta ne
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:39.86,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"issho ni kaerou"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:48.80,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\an8}aa hanabi ga yozora kirei ni saite chotto setsunaku
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:55.39,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\an8}aa kaze ga jikan to tomo ni nagareru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:22:02.67,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ureshikute tanoshikute bouken mo iro iro shita ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:09.34,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\an8}futari no himitsu no kichi no naka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:16.89,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kimi to natsu no owari shourai no yume ookina kibou wasurenai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:23.98,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}jyuunen no ato hachigatsu mata deaeru no wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:31.16,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kimi ga saigo made kokoro kara "arigatou" sakendeita koto shitetayo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.32,0:22:33.99,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}namida wo koraete egao
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:38.21,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}de sayounara setsunai yo ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:45.46,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}saikou no omoide wo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:48.80,Ending,,0,0,0,,The fireworks blossomed heartrendingly beautiful across the night sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:55.39,Ending,,0,0,0,,and time passed as swiftly as the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:30.53,Ending,,0,0,0,,We met in an unexpected moment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:37.19,Ending,,0,0,0,,when you called out to me at the crosswalk,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:39.86,Ending,,0,0,0,,"Let's walk home together."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:22:02.67,Ending,,0,0,0,,We shared so many happy times and thrilling adventures
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:09.34,Ending,,0,0,0,,together in our secret base.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:16.89,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,I will never forget the hopes and dreams we shared during that one summer's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:23.98,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we will meet again in another August, in maybe ten years time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:31.16,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,I could feel your heartfelt thanks all the way until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.32,0:22:33.99,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,And I know it must've been painful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:38.21,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,to hold back your tears and say goodbye with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:45.46,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,But those are my best memories.
